f; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;">Llenarla de luz, &nbsp;&nbsp;tomar el aire, <o:p></o:p></span></div><div class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%;"></div><div class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: &quot;palatino linotype&quot; , serif; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;">Y abandonar el frío.<o:p></o:p></span></div><div class="blogger-post-footer"><iframe width="150" height="350" src="http://adv.blogupp.com/code778ff9ad-58bd-4d23-a449-f0a3d4ab4f5d2v" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight ="0"></iframe></div>";s:4:"link";s:55:"http://introacrata.blogspot.com/2017/11/mano-vacia.html";s:6:"author";s:35:"noreply@blogger.com (Lotus Salcedo)";s:7:"summary";s:7095:"<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-vEfLf9afwlE/WgJFv3lxGvI/AAAAAAAADIs/4RJwS0TBYx4OXLPtOq5B0Qskdzn5LWRUQCLcBGAs/s1600/mano%2Bvac%25C3%25ADa-5.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="652" data-original-width="826" height="315" src="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-vEfLf9afwlE/WgJFv3lxGvI/AAAAAAAADIs/4RJwS0TBYx4OXLPtOq5B0Qskdzn5LWRUQCLcBGAs/s400/mano%2Bvac%25C3%25ADa-5.jpg" width="400" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"></div><div class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: &quot;palatino linotype&quot; , serif; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;">Abrir el puño <o:p></o:p></span></div><div class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: &quot;palatino linotype&quot; , serif; font-size